{\b #{\footnote html_patterns.htm_top}Pattern Window}\sa240\par\pard\plain
The following commands are available in the pattern window: 
\par\par\pard\plain
\fi-380\li380\tx380 {\f2\'b7}\tab {\uldb New Pattern}{\v html_patterns.htm_new} \par\pard\plain
\fi-380\li380\tx380 {\f2\'b7}\tab {\uldb Play Pattern}{\v html_patterns.htm_play} \par\pard\plain
